===========

PostgreSQL stores all Odoo business data.
odoo18db is your Odoo database.
res_partner stores contacts (customers, suppliers, companies, etc.).
res_users stores Odoo user accounts.
\l lists databases.
\dt lists tables.
\d table_name describes a table.
SELECT retrieves data.
\q exits PostgreSQL.


